# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# .gitignore — copied verbatim by genesis in Phase 1, then trimmed to the stack.
#
# KEEP ALWAYS (every genesis repo, stack-agnostic):
#   · Operating systems   · Editors / IDEs   · Secrets & env   · Logs
#   · Caches & coverage    · Temp & archives   · Scratch space
# APPEND PER STACK (Phase 4, only the chosen ones): Node · Python · Rust · Go ·
#   .NET · Java/Gradle · Infra (Terraform).
#
# Two rules that must never be violated:
#   1. NEVER ignore documented examples — `.env.example`, `.scratch/README.md`.
#   2. NEVER commit a secret. If a pattern below is too broad and hides a file
#      you need, narrow it — do not loosen the secret rules.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────


# ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Operating systems  (KEEP ALWAYS)
# ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

