# ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Scratch space  (KEEP ALWAYS — ephemeral work area defined in AGENTS.md §6)
#   Ignore everything inside `.scratch/` EXCEPT its README so the folder, its
#   purpose, and the documentation gate survive in git.
# ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
.scratch/*
!.scratch/README.md


